   <body>
      <div>
         <p>As an option, it is possible to add a panel heater inside
the cabinet. The panel heater is fixed with screws.</p>
         <p>For a set
temperature, the heater is turned on if the temperature is below or
turned off it the temperature is above.</p>
         <p>The supply for the heater
is connected to a push-in terminal. It needs to be connected to an
external supply on the customer site.</p>
         <note href="Panel_Light_CPT_DD00681585.xml#PanelLight-C4EF03C4/ForDetailsOnTheConnectionPleaseSeeT-C4EF6112">For details on the connection please see the <i>Terminal Diagrams</i>.</note>
